 "name": "RPlog_Retribution_-_A_Risky_Plan_for_the_Orphans",
 "title": "Retribution: A Risky Plan for the Orphans",
 "summary": "Amid the battle for Coruscant, the young pilot Aramis Tyrese sends General Luke Skywalker a halting, corrupted message about a desperate plan and a group of endangered children -- orphans -- caught up in the fighting, asking for guidance should things go wrong. As the New Republic forces, including Aramis, Keline, and Crash, weigh their risky options in space and on the ground, the fate of the vulnerable orphans hangs in the balance. The log sets up a perilous gambit to protect the children amid the wider war of retribution over the capital.",
